item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - SEVENTEEN - 10th Mini Album 'FML' (Bugs! FLAC 24bits/96kHz)
item.description:
FML is the 10th mini album by SEVENTEEN. It was released on April 24, 2023 with "F*ck My Life" and "Super" serving as the album's double title tracks.
The physical album comes in four versions: A (Fallen, Misfit, Lost), B (Faded Mono Life), C (Fight for My Life), Carat and Kit.
